{"tid":1762761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人做哨兵真係好易被自殺","createTime":"2019-11-29T21:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T14:09:37.000Z","uid":12110,"like":278,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"6ebb07dee8acf51fee076366ec42b3d4c3761732","tid":1762761,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T21:36:51.000Z","msg":"話我疑心重都係咁講<br />\n呢幾個月好多單停車場離奇跳樓<br />\n如果手足係一個人做哨兵係停車場要小心<br />\n唔好黑色黑褲/ 要街坊look<br />\n時刻留意身邊有冇異常<br />\n做哨之前要通知信得過嘅人<br />\n<br />\n周同學/荃灣同岩岩天水圍又一單<br />\n都係停車場跳樓<br />\n唔排除被自殺<br />\n被自殺係中共嘅手段黎恐嚇人 但又唔會明目張膽嘅手法<br />\n<br />\n當我多疑，手足請萬事小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"fd08bfd0ec671269bec99705f054d3a9d7ca93bf","tid":1762761,"uid":12110,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T21:37:44.000Z","msg":"小心駛得萬年船"},{"pid":"353c2e01908ac853fea33beae98a66e90dcdb78d","tid":1762761,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T21:38:21.000Z","msg":"手足請小心"},{"pid":"fb0cf5a52f8ea96363d07b792a5c8c76ba21fa46","tid":1762761,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T21:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a7676a8c567f4e1f0b65245ff089caa3b19115","tid":1762761,"uid":284858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T21:39:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8af5e04b85220d7a0f86e9707e4dc041ac0e1188","tid":1762761,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T21:46:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec929b4e1c2adcdb3795d9e354b526e838282e0c","tid":1762761,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T21:49:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13ef69e743743084d9522bcb2a36c34ba00670c9","tid":1762761,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T21:54:05.000Z","msg":"Pus"},{"pid":"85125392473218bf9673af7c7f905a5b0b4dd7b